And the algorithm takes note of your behavior to keep feeding you content that you are likely to interact with...

Anyway, this is a snippet of an hour long interview I did with @startcanadapodcast 2 weeks ago where we talked about social media marketing for entrepreneurs.

Go check out their page @startcanadapodcast 👈to see the full episode if you want some free tips on growing your business utilizing social media as a tool. 📲
